arguments.template:
<ion-header>
      <setting-navbar></setting-navbar>
      <ion-toolbar color="white">
        <ion-title>{{'setting.language' | translate}}</ion-title>
      </ion-toolbar>
    </ion-header>

    <ion-content>
      <ion-list>
        <ion-item *ngFor="let l of langList" (click)="langChange(l)" tappable>
          <ion-icon name="globe" item-left>
            <ion-icon name="checkmark-circle-filled" color="balanced" *ngIf="l.lang==language"></ion-icon>
          </ion-icon>
          <ion-label>{{'language.'+l.lang | translate}}</ion-label>
        </ion-item>
      </ion-list>
    </ion-content>
